## 🔧 Troubleshooting

**Dashboard not showing data?**
- Verify your data was successfully uploaded to Splunk
- Check that index name and sourcetype match your configuration
- Ensure sufficient data exists in the time range

**Import errors?**
- Validate XML syntax
- Check Splunk permissions for dashboard creation
- Verify compatible Splunk version

